function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	-- Ambush
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Snake", idActorPlayer)
	
	-- Drop key on last prisoner rescued
	if Hydra.QuestCallbackCountGet(2) == 4 then
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorGizmo, S_KEY_TREASURECLASS, idActorPlayer)
	end
	
end
